SECTION 31. IC 15-16-2-32, AS AMENDED BY P.L.81-2009,
SECTION 19, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 32. (a) The bag or other container in which any
commercial fertilizer is offered for sale, sold, or distributed in Indiana
must have a written or printed statement of the net weight and the
information required by section 31 of this chapter directly on or affixed
to the package.
