(1) written material;
(2) printed material;
(3) graphic material; or
HEA 1361 — Concur

44
(4) any other statement;
accompanying a fertilizer.
SECTION 46. IC 15-16-3-4 IS REPEALED [EFFECTIVE JULY 1,
